snippet.title: What Amber Heard & Johnny Depp's Situation says about Society
snippet.description:
Amber Heard & Johnny Depp’s domestic abuse case recently released new leaked audio recordings that imply Amber Heard being the true abuser. 

Whether this is about Gender; Men’s rights or Feminism (#metoo), it definitely sheds light on psychological, narcissistic abuse where the recordings display examples of gaslighting & other verbal abuse. thoughts?
